<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="no-js">
<head>
<%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>
<body class="<%= bodyClass %>">

<%- include('partials/preloader') %>
<%- include('partials/cursor') %>
<%- include('partials/nav') %>
<%- include('partials/whatsapp-float') %>

<main id="smooth-wrapper">
<div id="smooth-content">

  <section class="contact-page section section--ivory">
    <div class="contact-page__grid">

      <div class="contact-page__form-col">
        <span class="eyebrow reveal-up">Start an Inquiry</span>
        <h1 class="contact-page__title reveal-up">Tell Us About<br>Your Occasion</h1>
        <p class="contact-page__intro reveal-up">Share a few details about your event — the date, the guest count, the story you want told — and our team will follow up within two business days. Whether you're planning a wedding reception, a brand activation, or a private dinner for a handful of guests, the first step is the same: a conversation, followed by a tasting at our atelier in Noida.</p>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn--wine reveal-up" data-inquire-trigger data-cursor="hover" data-track-event="contact_page_cta_click">
          <span>Open Inquiry Form</span>
        </button>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-page__details-col">
        <div class="contact-page__image">
          <img src="<%= contactOfficeImage %>" alt="The Virtuoso Catering House atelier and tasting room" loading="lazy">
        </div>
        <div class="contact-details">
          <div class="contact-details__group">
            <span class="eyebrow eyebrow--gold">Atelier &amp; Tasting Room</span>
            <p>A-15, A-Block, Sector 61<br>Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201301</p>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-details__group">
            <span class="eyebrow eyebrow--gold">Reach Us</span>
            <p><a href="mailto:virtuosocatering@gmail.com" data-track-event="contact_page_email_click">virtuosocatering@gmail.com</a><br>
            <a href="tel:+918700915463" data-track-event="contact_page_phone_click">+91 87009 15463</a></p>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-details__group">
            <span class="eyebrow eyebrow--gold">Hours</span>
            <p>Tastings by appointment<br>Tuesday — Saturday, 10am–6pm</p>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-details__group">
            <div class="contact-map">
              <iframe
                src="https://www.google.com/maps?q=A-15,+A-Block,+Sector+61,+Noida,+Uttar+Pradesh+201301&output=embed"
                title="Map showing the Virtuoso Catering House atelier location in Noida"
                loading="lazy"
                referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
                allowfullscreen>
              </iframe>
            </div>
            <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/VztH6YKQfN13Yogu7" class="link-underline contact-map__link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-cursor="hover">View on Google Maps</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT HAPPENS NEXT -->
  <section class="contact-next section section--ivory">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="eyebrow reveal-up">What Happens Next</span>
        <h2 class="section-title reveal-up">From Inquiry to Tasting</h2>
        <span class="section-header__line"></span>
      </div>
      <div class="blog-post__prose">
        <p class="blog-post__copy reveal-up">Once you submit an inquiry, someone from the Virtuoso team reviews the details and follows up within two business days — usually with a short call to talk through the date, the guest count, and the shape of the event before anything is put on paper. From there, we schedule a private tasting at our atelier in Sector 61, Noida, where you'll work through menu direction in person rather than over email.</p>
        <p class="blog-post__copy reveal-up">A written proposal follows the tasting, covering the menu, service format, and pricing for your guest count. There's no obligation at the inquiry stage — it's simply the fastest way to get a real conversation started, whether you're six months out from a wedding or finalizing a brand activation on a tighter timeline.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
</div>
</main>

<%- include('partials/scripts') %>
</body>
</html>
